ity takeoff restrictions, runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) and 6 others. Changed since last run: Bergen Airport, Flesland (BGO/ENBR), Oslo-Gardermoen (OSL/ENGM), Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO), Olsztyn-Mazury (SZY/EPSY), Bucharest Băneasa Aurel Vlaicu (BBU/LRBS), Bucharest Henri Coandă (OTP/LROP), Dubai (DXB/OMDB), Gdańsk Lech Wałęsa (GDN/EPGD), Warsaw Chopin (WAW/EPWA), Ljubljana Jože Pučnik (LJU/LJLJ) and 2 others.",
